        {"speaker": "A", "roman": "ii tinglu puurti hiigee iratta ?", "english": "Will it be like this throughout this month ?"},
        {"speaker": "B", "roman": "haudu, ii tinglu heccu-kammie caliinee", "english": "Yes, it is mostly cold this month."},
